# User-level communication (global)

**Canonical files** (resolve `~` to your home directory; they apply in every project when present):

- **`~/.cursor/rules/communication-base.mdc`** — baseline standards you edit; not overwritten by automation.
- **`~/.cursor/rules/communication-learned.mdc`** — merged by **`/communication-style`** from **`~/.cursor/projects/*/agent-transcripts/*.jsonl`**.

Honor those files for plan structure and reply style. On a new machine, copy **`templates/*.mdc`** from this plugin’s repo into **`~/.cursor/rules/`**, then run **`/communication-style`**.
